, all named with Old English <i>strǣt</i> ‘paved road, street’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘farmstead, estate’. Compare   Stratton  ."]}]},{"name":"Margery","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["The usual medieval vernacular form of   Margaret   (now also commonly spelled   Marjorie  ). This form of the name is preserved in the nursery rhyme ‘See-saw, Margery Daw’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Margery Stratton was born in 1302, in Staunton, Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Sir Geoffrey de Staunton about 1318. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1319, in Shotley, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 17."},"et":{"1302–1319":"1302–1319","1302–1369":"1302–1369","1320–1360":"1320–1360","1369":"1369","1302":"1302","1320":"1320","1360":"1360","1319":"1319","ABT 1318":"umbes 1318","Shotley, Suffolk (England)":"Shotley, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Staunton, Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Staunton, Nottinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1302–1319":"1302–1319","1302–1369":"1302–1369","1320–1360":"1320–1360","1369":"1369","1302":"1302","1320":"1320","1360":"1360","1319":"1319","ABT 1318":"noin 1318","Shotley, Suffolk (England)":"Shotley, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Staunton, Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Staunton, Nottinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1302–1319":"1302–1319","1302–1369":"1302–1369","1320–1360":"1320–1360","1369":"1369","1302":"1302","1320":"1320","1360":"1360","1319":"1319","ABT 1318":"environ 1318","Shotley, Suffolk (England)":"Shotley, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Staunton, Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Staunton, Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Margery Stratton est née en 1302, à Staunton, Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Sir Geoffrey de Staunton environ 1318. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. 